# Contact form email delivery (Resend — https://resend.com)
# Create a free account, add an API key, and (for production) verify a sending domain.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Where contact form submissions are delivered.
# Defaults to the business email in src/lib/site.ts if unset.
# NOTE: with the test sender below, this MUST be the Resend account owner's
# own email, or Resend will reject the send. Verify a domain to send anywhere.
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=

# Verified sender. Until a domain is verified in Resend, you can use their
# shared test sender below — but it ONLY delivers to the Resend account owner's
# own email. To deliver to anyone else (e.g. Ramcorpmanagement@gmail.com),
# verify a sending domain in Resend and use an address on that domain.
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL="Broadway The Lyricist <onboarding@resend.dev>"
